com.ibm.team.process.common.advice

Interface IObjectsResponse


  • public interface IObjectsResponse
    Operation response which carries a collection of data transfer objects (EObject).

    This response object should not be used for persisted, modeled objects.

    IItemsResponse should be used to transmit persisted objects.

    Since:
    0.5
